doctor.name: Dr. Md. Helalur Rahman
doctor.info: Dr. Md. Helalur Rahman is a Medicine Specialist in Comilla. His qualification is MBBS, BCS (Health), FCPS (Medicine), Higher Training (Neuromedicine). He is a Assistant Professor, Department of Medicine at Cumilla Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at CD Path & Hospital Pvt. Ltd.. Practicing hour of Dr. Md. Helalur Rahman at CD Path & Hospital Pvt. Ltd. is 2pm to 9pm (Closed: Friday).

doctor.name: Dr. Amrit Kumar Debnath
doctor.info: Dr. Amrit Kumar Debnath is a Medicine Specialist in Comilla. His qualification is MBBS, FCPS (Medicine), MACP (USA). He is a Consultant, Department of Medicine at General Hospital, Cumilla. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Comilla Trauma Center. Practicing hour of Dr. Amrit Kumar Debnath at Comilla Trauma Center is 3pm to 9pm (Sat to Wed) & 9am to 3pm (Fri).
